OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777993872
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's
OL,4,C#78bn loan scheme for Ukraine
OL,6,FThe UK intends to start talks to join
OL,7,Fthe European Union's 90 billion euro
OL,8,F(#78 billion) loan for Ukraine, as the
OL,9,Fgovernment seeks to bolster support
OL,10,Ffor Kyiv and deepen defence ties with
OL,11,Fthe bloc.
OL,13,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer will tell
OL,14,Fleaders at a European gathering in
OL,15,FArmenia's capital Yerevan on Monday
OL,16,Fthat Britain wants to work more
OL,17,Fclosely with them to ensure Ukraine
OL,18,Fgets the military equipment it needs
OL,19,Fto continue its fightback against
OL,20,FRussia's invasion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777993872
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's
OL,4,C#78bn loan scheme for Ukraine
OL,6,FThe bid to participate in the loan
OL,7,Fscheme ` recently approved by the EU
OL,8,Fafter Viktor Orban's defeat in
OL,9,FHungarian elections ended a long-
OL,10,Frunning impasse ` is part of the prime
OL,11,Fminister's reset with Brussels.
OL,13,FStarmer called for the UK and EU to
OL,14,F"go further and faster on defence" co-
OL,15,Foperation before his visit to the
OL,16,FEuropean Political Community summit
OL,17,F(EPC) in Armenia, only the second by a
OL,18,FBritish leader to the Caucasus country
OL,19,Fand the first in more than 25 years.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
