OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777993872
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's
OL,4,C#78bn loan scheme for Ukraine
OL,6,FHe also noted access to the initiative
OL,7,Fcould create opportunities for British
OL,8,Fdefence firms to compete for contracts
OL,9,Funder the scheme.
OL,11,FThe UK will also put further sanctions
OL,12,Fon Russian companies to disrupt
OL,13,Fmilitary supply chains later this
OL,14,Fweek, according to Downing Street.
OL,16,FStarmer said: "When the UK and the
OL,17,FEuropean Union work together, we all
OL,18,Freap the benefits ` and in these
OL,19,Fvolatile times we need to go further
OL,20,Fand faster on defence to keep people
OL,21,Fsafe.
OL,26,@xD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777993872
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's
OL,4,C#78bn loan scheme for Ukraine
OL,6,F"That is why we are beginning
OL,7,Fnegotiations with the EU to ensure
OL,8,FUkraine gets the equipment it needs to
OL,9,Fdefend its freedom, while driving
OL,10,Fopportunities for British industry to
OL,11,Fplay its full part.
OL,13,F"I will always act in our national
OL,14,Finterest: protecting our security,
OL,15,Fsupporting our allies, and delivering
OL,16,Fjobs and stability at home."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
