PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777993872
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's
OL,4,C#78bn loan scheme for Ukraine
OL,6,FThe UK and EU, which will hold another
OL,7,Fjoint summit this summer, will
OL,8,Fnegotiate the parameters of access to
OL,9,Fthe bloc's loan for Ukraine in the
OL,10,Fcoming weeks, No 10 said.
OL,12,FThe EU last month approved the
OL,13,Ffinancial boost, vital to keep Ukraine
OL,14,Fafloat for the next two years, after
OL,15,FHungary lifted its veto.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
