PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777993872
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's
OL,4,C#78bn loan scheme for Ukraine
OL,6,FStarmer is expected to hold meetings
OL,7,Fwith some of his European counterparts
OL,8,Fin the margins of the EPC, with
OL,9,FUkrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky
OL,10,Falso set to attend.
OL,12,FThe meeting of the EPC, formed in 2022
OL,13,Fafter Moscow's full-scale invasion of
OL,14,FUkraine, comes as US President Donald
OL,15,FTrump has shifted his attention from
OL,16,Fthat conflict to the one in the Middle
OL,17,FEast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
