FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777993872
OL,3,CUK to enter talks on joining EU's
OL,4,C#78bn loan scheme for Ukraine
OL,6,FThe fallout from the Iran war will
OL,7,Falso be high on the agenda, and the
OL,8,Fprime minister will press for action
OL,9,Fto limit the economic impacts and de-
OL,10,Fescalate.
OL,12,FHe will discuss with allies how to
OL,13,Fbest contribute to long-term security
OL,14,Fin the Strait of Hormuz, a key oil and
OL,15,Fgas shipping route whose blockade has
OL,16,Fstrained economies worldwide.
OL,18,FThe prime minister's trip comes before
OL,19,Flocal elections this week when voters
OL,20,Fwill deliver their first verdict on
OL,21,Fhis government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
